Package org.opengis.cite.geomatics

Enum Class SpatialOperator

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SpatialOperator>
org.opengis.cite.geomatics.SpatialOperator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SpatialOperator>, Constable
public enum SpatialOperator extends Enum<SpatialOperator>
Named spatial relationship predicates based on the dimensionally extended nine-intersection matrix (DE-9IM) and ISO 19143 (OGC 09-026r2). The Beyond and DWithin predicates are derived from the analytic method Distance(Geometry g1, Geometry g2), which returns the minimum distance between two geometries.
